service car
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a form of passenger transport in rural areas [by which goods and services were also delivered and collected in small settlements.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: aka service-car
Citations
